# Typography System

Complete typography guidelines for EstateHero component library.

## Font Families

### Current Setup (IBM Plex - Placeholder)

```typescript
fontFamily: {
  sans: ['IBM Plex Sans', 'system-ui', '-apple-system', 'sans-serif'],
  serif: ['IBM Plex Serif', 'Georgia', 'serif'],
  mono: ['IBM Plex Mono', 'Courier New', 'monospace'],
}
```

### Production Fonts (Future)

When ready to switch to production fonts:

```typescript
fontFamily: {
  sans: ['Elza Text', 'system-ui', '-apple-system', 'sans-serif'],
  serif: ['Georgia', 'serif'],
  mono: ['RM Mono TRIAL', 'Courier New', 'monospace'],
}
```

## Font Family Usage

### font-sans (Primary)

**Used for:** Body text, UI components, buttons, labels, most text

```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT - Default, no need to specify
<p className="text-base">Body text uses sans by default</p>

// Explicit usage (rarely needed)
<p className="font-sans">Explicit sans-serif</p>
```

### font-serif (Decorative)

**Used for:** Decorative headings, hero text, emphasis

```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT - For decorative headings
<h1 className="font-serif text-4xl">Hero Heading</h1>
<h2 className="font-serif text-2xl">Section Title</h2>
```

### font-mono (Technical)

**Used for:** Code blocks, technical data, monospace content

```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT - Code and technical content
<code className="font-mono text-sm">const value = true;</code>
<pre className="font-mono text-xs">API Response</pre>
```

## Font Weights

### Available Weights

| Weight | Value | Tailwind Class | Usage |
|--------|-------|----------------|-------|
| Regular | 400 | `font-normal` | Body text, default |
| Medium | 500 | `font-medium` | Buttons, labels, emphasis |
| Semibold | 600 | `font-semibold` | Subheadings, strong emphasis |
| Bold | 700 | `font-bold` | Headings, important text |

### Weight Usage Patterns

```tsx
// Body text - Regular (400)
<p className="font-normal">Standard body text</p>

// Buttons - Medium (500)
<button className="font-medium">Click me</button>

// Subheadings - Semibold (600)
<h3 className="font-semibold">Section Title</h3>

// Main headings - Bold (700)
<h1 className="font-bold">Page Title</h1>
```

## Font Sizes & Line Heights

### Size Scale

| Name | Class | Size | Line Height | Usage |
|------|-------|------|-------------|-------|
| Extra Small | `text-xs` | 0.75rem (12px) | 1rem (16px) | Captions, helper text |
| Small | `text-sm` | 0.875rem (14px) | 1.25rem (20px) | Small body, buttons |
| Base | `text-base` | 1rem (16px) | 1.5rem (24px) | Default body text |
| Large | `text-lg` | 1.125rem (18px) | 1.75rem (28px) | Large body, intro text |
| XL | `text-xl` | 1.25rem (20px) | 1.75rem (28px) | H4 headings |
| 2XL | `text-2xl` | 1.5rem (24px) | 2rem (32px) | H3 headings |
| 3XL | `text-3xl` | 1.875rem (30px) | 2.25rem (36px) | H2 headings |
| 4XL | `text-4xl` | 2.25rem (36px) | 2.5rem (40px) | H1 headings |
| 5XL | `text-5xl` | 3rem (48px) | 1 | Hero text |
| 6XL | `text-6xl` | 3.75rem (60px) | 1 | Large hero text |

## Typography Patterns

### Headings

```tsx
// H1 - Page title
<h1 className="text-4xl font-bold text-foreground">
  Page Title
</h1>

// H2 - Section heading
<h2 className="text-3xl font-bold text-foreground">
  Section Heading
</h2>

// H3 - Subsection heading
<h3 className="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">
  Subsection Heading
</h3>

// H4 - Minor heading
<h4 className="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">
  Minor Heading
</h4>

// Decorative heading (with serif)
<h1 className="font-serif text-5xl font-bold text-foreground">
  Hero Title
</h1>
```

### Body Text

```tsx
// Standard body
<p className="text-base text-foreground">
  Standard paragraph text
</p>

// Large body (intro text)
<p className="text-lg text-foreground">
  Introduction or lead paragraph
</p>

// Small body
<p className="text-sm text-foreground">
  Secondary information
</p>

// Caption text
<p className="text-xs text-muted-foreground">
  Caption or helper text
</p>
```

### Labels & UI Text

```tsx
// Form label
<label className="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">
  Label Text
</label>

// Button text
<button className="text-sm font-medium">
  Button Text
</button>

// Helper text
<span className="text-xs text-muted-foreground">
  Helper text or hint
</span>

// Error message
<span className="text-sm text-destructive">
  Error message
</span>
```

### Links

```tsx
// Standard link
<a className="text-base text-primary underline hover:text-primary/90">
  Link Text
</a>

// Inline link
<p className="text-base">
  This is a paragraph with an{" "}
  <a className="text-primary underline hover:text-primary/90">
    inline link
  </a>
  .
</p>

// Button-style link
<a className="text-sm font-medium text-primary hover:text-primary/90">
  Navigation Link
</a>
```

### Code & Technical

```tsx
// Inline code
<code className="font-mono text-sm bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">
  inline code
</code>

// Code block
<pre className="font-mono text-xs bg-muted p-4 rounded-md overflow-x-auto">
  <code>const example = true;</code>
</pre>

// Technical data
<span className="font-mono text-sm text-muted-foreground">
  #FF5733
</span>
```

